== 文化 ==
列治文的[[史提夫斯頓|史提夫斯頓]]村每年於[[加拿大日|加拿大日]]（7月1日）都會舉行[[鮭魚|鮭魚]]節。屆時在史提夫斯頓社區中心外面會擺賣烤鮭魚和舉行[[嘉年華會|嘉年華會]]。各級政府的本地政治代表都經常以參加加拿大日遊行或派發[[加拿大國旗|加拿大國旗]]的形式出席這項活動。

2002年8月8日到12日期間史提夫斯頓主辦了[[大帆船|大帆船]]節。估計在這5天裡面一共吸引了400,000人到史提夫斯頓。這個活動的成功超越了本來的預期，但同時卻給這個平靜的社區帶來交通混亂<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.richmond-news.com/issues02/082202/news/082202nn2.html |title=Richmond News: "Richmond Tall Ships 2002 attracts 400,000 people"（英文） |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050123045136/http://www.richmond-news.com/issues02/082202/news/082202nn2.html |archivedate=2005-01-23 |accessdate=2006-06-20 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.richmond-news.com/issues02/082202/news/082202nn8.html |title=Richmond News: "'Holy mackerel,' tall ships festival draws huge crowd"（英文） |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050123034051/http://www.richmond-news.com/issues02/082202/news/082202nn8.html |archivedate=2005-01-23 |accessdate=2006-06-20 }}</ref>。由於停車場不足的緣故，本地的居民便想到以售賣私人車道和前院作停車空間生財<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.richmond-news.com/issues02/082202/news/082202nn6.html|title=Richmond News: "Parking woes lead to anger and profits"（英文）|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070926231805/http://www.richmond-news.com/issues02/082202/news/082202nn6.html|archivedate=2007-09-26|accessdate=2006-06-20}}</ref>。儘管這次活動很受歡迎，但它帶來的收入卻彌補不了開支，所以市政府決定從此不再舉行這類型的活動<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.royalcityrecord.com/issues03/104203/news/104203nn2.html |title=Royal City Record: "Small - but Tall - better"（英文） |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070517060636/http://www.royalcityrecord.com/issues03/104203/news/104203nn2.html |archivedate=2007-05-17 |accessdate=2006-06-20 }}</ref>。

夏天期間列治文有一年一度的「列治文[[夜市|夜市]]」。夜市裡會擺賣各種各樣的商品與食物，更有些現場表演。這大型夜市每年都吸引很多[[低陸平原|低陸平原]]的居民參觀。

加拿大電視業界盛事[[双子座奖|双子座奖]]的2006年度頒獎典禮於列治文舉行，是該項頒獎典禮首次由加拿大西岸的城市舉行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cknw.com/news/news_local.cfm?cat=7428327912&rem=34161&red=80132723aPBIny&wids=410&gi=1&gm=news_local.cfm |title=CKNW AM 980: "Richmond's River Rock Casino to host this year's Gemini Awards"（英文） |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070514173809/http://www.cknw.com/news/news_local.cfm?cat=7428327912&rem=34161&red=80132723aPBIny&wids=410&gi=1&gm=news_local.cfm |archivedate=2007-05-14 |accessdate=2006-06-20 }}</ref>。

